li>\n<li>Select: <code class=\"language-text\">↓</code> key opens the dropdown, <code class=\"language-text\">↑</code> <code class=\"language-text\">↓</code> keys navigate, <code class=\"language-text\">Enter</code> selects</li>\n<li>Tree: <code class=\"language-text\">↑</code> <code class=\"language-text\">↓</code> keys navigate, <code class=\"language-text\">→</code> expands child nodes, <code class=\"language-text\">←</code> collapses child nodes</li>\n<li>Lov: <code class=\"language-text\">↓</code> opens the popup, <code class=\"language-text\">↑</code> <code class=\"language-text\">↓</code> keys navigate</li>\n<li>Switch: <code class=\"language-text\">←</code> <code class=\"language-text\">→</code> keys toggle on and off</li>\n<li>Range: <code class=\"language-text\">←</code> <code class=\"language-text\">→</code> keys move the slider</li>\n<li>IntlField: <code class=\"language-text\">↓</code> opens the popup</li>\n<li>\n<p>The following component shortcuts <strong>depend on whether keyboard control is enabled</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>NumberField: <code class=\"language-text\">↑</code> <code class=\"language-text\">↓</code> keys increment or decrement the value</li>\n<li>Tabs: <code class=\"language-text\">↑</code> <code class=\"language-text\">↓</code> <code class=\"language-text\">←</code> <code class=\"language-text\">→</code> keys switch panels</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"space-key\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#space-key\" aria-label=\"space key permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Space Key</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Lov / Select / DatePicker: Opens the dropdown panel</li>\n<li>Switch: Toggles the component on or off</li>\n<li>Checkbox: Checks or unchecks the box</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"other-shortcuts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#other-shortcuts\" aria-label=\"other shortcuts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Other Shortcuts</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Modal: <code class=\"language-text\">esc</code> key closes the modal (<strong>depends on keyboardClosable setting</strong>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"table-shortcut-support-depends-on-whether-keyboard-control-is-enabled\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#table-shortcut-support-depends-on-whether-keyboard-control-is-enabled\" aria-label=\"table shortcut support depends on whether keyboard control is enabled permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table Shortcut Support (<strong>depends on whether keyboard control is enabled</strong>)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Alt   n</code>: With focus in a table cell (not in the query bar), add a new row (can be configured to add at the top or bottom, only supported for inline editing)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl   s</code>: When focus is in a table cell, save the current table</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl   d</code> (or <code class=\"language-text\">Command   d</code>):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Focus in a table cell copies the cell content from the previous row</li>\n<li>Focus on a table row copies all cell contents from the previous row</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Delete</code>: Deletes one character if the current element is focused</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Alt   delete</code>: With focus in a table cell, deletes the current row, with a confirmation popup</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Shift + Arrow keys</code>: When the focus is on a row in the table and the current table allows multiple selections, you can select multiple rows</li>\n</ul>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"choerodon-ui"}]},{"type":"text","value":" Component Keyboard Shortcuts Documentation"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"common-shortcuts","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#common-shortcuts","ariaLabel":"common shortcuts permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9z